Exchange Rates API (1.0)

Download OpenAPI specification:Download

Fluentax: hello@fluentax.com URL: https://www.fluentax.com/contact-us

Exchange Rates API for retrieving daily, weekly, biweekly, and monthly currency exchange rates from official sources (central banks, tax authorities). Visit our website to find up-to-date information on the supported data sources and detailed API features.

Find out more on our Developer Portal
